-08-23T17:01:15.000Z","msg":"個或然率仲低過0啊"},{"pid":"f6bd7bc432a31856258c495470af5c4dcb9a94a2","tid":791274,"uid":65598,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T17:04:45.000Z","msg":"知唔知乜撚野叫期望值呀？"},{"pid":"8db83cb176e77befe3bcbc247a8099bf2e3dffc5","tid":791274,"uid":75610,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"e1fb772cb0e209b394c4d8715ff19a67dcc5abf4","tid":791274,"uid":63843,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T17:01:15.000Z","msg":"個或然率仲低過0啊"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T17:26:43.000Z","msg":"我都淨係諗到少林足球"},{"pid":"eda32f1090bda95dfa85fdc4dd17fad51f71627b","tid":791274,"uid":87155,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T17:36:58.000Z","msg":"屌 個銀仔一係公係一字 永遠無中間嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50891dba03cb001f01991c4dfbac144a7531f55f","tid":791274,"uid":63952,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T17:53:02.000Z","msg":"人人期望可達到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4095f8ef489a03364b1efc48669ef52f1139b7dd","tid":791274,"uid":184233,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T17:57:23.000Z","msg":"樓主係我表弟<br />\n佢有中度弱智<br />\n大家比條生路佢<br />\n佢仲服用緊精神科藥物"},{"pid":"73f52329b200a9d4b497b2fd4e6945b66520a64e","tid":791274,"uid":130568,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T17:58:04.000Z","msg":"擲同一塊銀仔10次，擲到5次公既機會率係24.61%<br />\n<br />\nPS: 亂答，唔知樓主講緊乜"},{"pid":"c75957e6b044eb60cc41c6a753ee6a9facaa3532","tid":791274,"uid":72465,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T18:18:11.000Z","msg":"樓主 D 語言邏輯亂到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係擲到公次數嘅期望值係 5<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9db0232b50917f5b2c3256700b209462aa175510","tid":791274,"uid":72465,"like":24,"dislike":4,"score":20,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T18:43:31.000Z","msg":"將每次擲銀仔當成一個 Bernoulli trial，當中擲到公嘅機率係 50%。<br />\n<br />\n呢個 Bernoulli trial 會重複 10 次，而喺呢 10 次入面擲到公嘅公嘅次數 X 就係一個 binomial random variable，當中 X = 0, 1, 2, 3, ..., 10<br />\n<br />\n計 x 次公機率嘅公式係呢條<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/24/023322_c7da2202001ef3739c67954b4c9dbb31.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F24%2F023322_c7da2202001ef3739c67954b4c9dbb31.PNG&h=1b898796&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n括號入面嘅 n x 其實係 nCr 嘅另一個寫法，即係 n 個入面抽 x 個有幾多 combination。<br />\n<br />\n呢如計 P(X = 5) = 10C5 * 0.5^5 * 0.5*5 = 0.2461<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上面已經有巴打計到<br />\n<br />\n另一個計法係用返中學嘅 concept<br />\nTotal sample space 有 2^10 = 1024 個 combinations<br />\n擲中 5 公 5 字嘅 combinations 係 10! / (5!5!) = 252<br />\n所以 P(X = 5) = 252 / 1024 = 0.2461<br />\n<br />\n如果將所有 P(X=0) P(X=1) ... P(X=10) 計晒出嚟 plot 喺幅 graph 度會得到一幅 binomial distribution。<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.dummies.com/wp-content/uploads/460747.image0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dummies.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F460747.image0.jpg&h=05b09e2a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而期望值，或者叫平均值，喺呢度講緊嘅係擲中公嘅次數，亦即係 10 * 0.5 = 5 次。"},{"pid":"b56abd4d3b317cc5d5e9672251fc998a34597949","tid":791274,"uid":118502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T18:44:38.000Z","msg":"擲幾多次唔撚關事"},{"pid":"dcc5c20c81ce650fae707c29dbd339679af94323","tid":791274,"uid":116578,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T18:45:46.000Z","msg":"買六合彩同一個道理 一係中 一係唔中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2eb3c464dcf421af11da88756c21d08527df4b21","tid":791274,"uid":176935,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T18:50:38.000Z","msg":"但係數學計唔到個幣停係中間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"856ce803edbadd988ebfdfa6e7cee993c8aa1024","tid":791274,"uid":194560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e1fb772cb0e209b394c4d8715ff19a67dcc5abf4","tid":791274,"uid":63843,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T17:01:15.000Z","msg":"個或然率仲低過0啊"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T19:23:16.000Z","msg":"個或然撚呢就"},{"pid":"8412f0b5a3065db667333f23f5d042a3441cfb40","tid":791274,"uid":1248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"856ce803edbadd988ebfdfa6e7cee993c8aa1024","tid":791274,"uid":194560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e1fb772cb0e209b394c4d8715ff19a67dcc5abf4","tid":791274,"uid":63843,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T17:01:15.000Z","msg":"個或然率仲低過0啊"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T19:23:16.000Z","msg":"個或然撚呢就"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T19:24:23.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">你個樣就撚</span>"},{"pid":"473508d22728909de8e43b8926a2b95fd61c48e1","tid":791274,"uid":72465,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T19:43:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>計 x 次公機率嘅公式係呢條<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/24/023322_c7da2202001ef3739c67954b4c9dbb31.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F24%2F023322_c7da2202001ef3739c67954b4c9dbb31.PNG&h=1b898796&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n括號入面嘅 n x 其實係 nCr 嘅另一個寫法，即係 n 個入面抽 x 個有幾多 combinations。<br />\n<br />\n呢如計 P(X = 5) = 10C5 * 0.5^5 * 0.5<span style=\"color: red;\">^</span>5 = 0.2461<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上面已經有巴打計到<br />\n</blockquote><br />\n屌原來我講漏咗<br />\np 係每擲中公嘅機率，q 係每次擲中字嘅機率，因為 p 同 q 係 complementary 所以 q = 1 - p。<br />\n<br />\n計多個例子。<br />\n如果要計擲到 2 次或以下公嘅機率 P(X &le; 2) <br />\n= P(X = 0) + P(X = 1) + P(X = 2)<br />\n= 10C0 * 0.5^0 * 0.5^10 + 10C1 * 0.5^1 * 0.5^9 + 10C2 * 0.5^2 * 0.5^8<br />\n= 0.0547"},{"pid":"72b7414c711deab1a0366549c840f187bbe6107d","tid":791274,"uid":14224,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"9db0232b50917f5b2c3256700b209462aa175510","tid":791274,"uid":72465,"like":24,"dislike":4,"score":20,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T18:43:31.000Z","msg":"將每次擲銀仔當成一個 Bernoulli trial，當中擲到公嘅機率係 50%。<br />\n<br />\n呢個 Bernoulli trial 會重複 10 次，而喺呢 10 次入面擲到公嘅公嘅次數 X 就係一個 binomial random variable，當中 X = 0, 1, 2, 3, ..., 10<br />\n<br />\n計 x 次公機率嘅公式係呢條<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/24/023322_c7da2202001ef3739c67954b4c9dbb31.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F24%2F023322_c7da2202001ef3739c67954b4c9dbb31.PNG&h=1b898796&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n括號入面嘅 n x 其實係 nCr 嘅另一個寫法，即係 n 個入面抽 x 個有幾多 combination。<br />\n<br />\n呢如計 P(X = 5) = 10C5 * 0.5^5 * 0.5*5 = 0.2461<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上面已經有巴打計到<br />\n<br />\n另一個計法係用返中學嘅 concept<br />\nTotal sample space 有 2^10 = 1024 個 combinations<br />\n擲中 5 公 5 字嘅 combinations 係 10! / (5!5!) = 252<br />\n所以 P(X = 5) = 252 / 1024 = 0.2461<br />\n<br />\n如果將所有 P(X=0) P(X=1) ... P(X=10) 計晒出嚟 plot 喺幅 graph 度會得到一幅 binomial distribution。<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.dummies.com/wp-content/uploads/460747.image0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dummies.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F460747.image0.jpg&h=05b09e2a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而期望值，或者叫平均值，喺呢度講緊嘅係擲中公嘅次數，亦即係 10 * 0.5 = 5 次。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T21:02:36.000Z","msg":"可能我認真咗<br />\n巴打你計錯晒喎"},{"pid":"dad64df4369643899d253c5cceff95e7d32745d7","tid":791274,"uid":72465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"72b7414c711deab1a0366549c840f187bbe6107d","tid":791274,"uid":14224,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"9db0232b50917f5b2c3256700b209462aa175510","tid":791274,"uid":72465,"like":24,"dislike":4,"score":20,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T18:43:31.000Z","msg":"將每次擲銀仔當成一個 Bernoulli trial，當中擲到公嘅機率係 50%。<br />\n<br />\n呢個 Bernoulli trial 會重複 10 次，而喺呢 10 次入面擲到公嘅公嘅次數 X 就係一個 binomial random variable，當中 X = 0, 1, 2, 3, ..., 10<br />\n<br />\n計 x 次公機率嘅公式係呢條<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/24/023322_c7da2202001ef3739c67954b4c9dbb31.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F24%2F023322_c7da2202001ef3739c67954b4c9dbb31.PNG&h=1b898796&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n括號入面嘅 n x 其實係 nCr 嘅另一個寫法，即係 n 個入面抽 x 個有幾多 combination。<br />\n<br />\n呢如計 P(X = 5) = 10C5 * 0.5^5 * 0.5*5 = 0.2461<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上面已經有巴打計到<br />\n<br />\n另一個計法係用返中學嘅 concept<br />\nTotal sample space 有 2^10 = 1024 個 combinations<br />\n擲中 5 公 5 字嘅 combinations 係 10! / (5!5!) = 252<br />\n所以 P(X = 5) = 252 / 1024 = 0.2461<br />\n<br />\n如果將所有 P(X=0) P(X=1) ... P(X=10) 計晒出嚟 plot 喺幅 graph 度會得到一幅 binomial distribution。<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.dummies.com/wp-content/uploads/460747.image0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dummies.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F460747.image0.jpg&h=05b09e2a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而期望值，或者叫平均值，喺呢度講緊嘅係擲中公嘅次數，亦即係 10 * 0.5 = 5 次。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T21:02:36.000Z","msg":"可能我認真咗<br />\n巴打你計錯晒喎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T21:18:46.000Z","msg":"咁應該係點計？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}